# 06. Financial System

Status: Approved for MVP

---

# Purpose

This document defines the complete financial architecture of Amazing Chance.

It describes how payments are processed, how funds are allocated, how immutable financial records are stored, and how financial integrity is guaranteed.

This document is the single source of truth for all money-related operations.

---

# Business Goal

Provide a transparent, secure and immutable financial system where every payment is traceable, every allocation is auditable, and no administrator can manipulate financial data.

---

# User Goal

Users should be able to:

- purchase tickets;
- receive prizes;
- view payment history;
- verify prize payments;
- trust that money cannot be altered.

---

# Scope

Included:

- Purchase Orders
- Payments
- Ticket Creation
- Financial Ledger
- Weekly Jackpot Allocation
- Annual Jackpot Allocation
- Company Revenue Allocation
- Prize Payments
- Refunds
- Financial Audit

Not Included:

- Draw Logic
- Random.org Integration
- Winner Selection
- User Authentication

Those modules are described in separate documents.

