# Core Principles

## Immutable Records Principle

Financial records can never be edited.

Corrections are performed only by creating new records.

---

## Ledger is the Single Source of Truth

Balances are never manually stored.

All financial values are calculated from immutable ledger records.

---

## Automatic Allocation

Every confirmed payment is automatically divided into:

70% → Weekly Jackpot

20% → Company Revenue

10% → Annual Jackpot

No manual allocation is allowed.

---

## No Internal Wallet

Amazing Chance does not use a deposit wallet.

Users never preload funds.

Every purchase is linked to a specific Purchase Order.

---

## No Administrative Financial Control

Administrators cannot:

- change balances;
- change jackpot amounts;
- edit payments;
- modify ledger records;
- create fake transactions;
- edit prize amounts.

Financial integrity is fully system-controlled.

