# UI Requirements

The Financial System is primarily a backend module.

Users may access the following financial information:

- Purchase History
- Payment Status
- Prize Payment History
- Refund History

The administration interface shall provide read-only financial reporting.

No interface shall allow modification of immutable financial records.

---

# Integration Points

The Financial System integrates with:

- User Management
- Purchase Order Module
- Payment Provider Module
- Ticket Module
- Draw Module
- Prize Module
- Audit Module
- Reporting Module

The Financial System does not determine draw results or winning tickets.

---

# Performance Requirements

- Payment confirmation shall be processed immediately after provider notification.
- Ticket generation shall complete within acceptable system response times.
- Financial allocation shall execute within the same transaction as ticket generation.
- Ledger writes shall be durable before transaction completion.
- Financial reports shall be generated from immutable ledger data.

---

# Dependencies

This module depends on:

- User Management
- Purchase Orders
- External Payment Providers
- Ticket Generation
- Audit Logging

This module is required before implementing:

- Draw Engine
- Prize Distribution
- Financial Reporting

